  "text": "The cyclic cohomology determined by the Λ-module C • H (δ,σ) is said to be the cyclic cohomology of the Hopf algebra H with respect to the modular pair (δ, σ) and will be denoted by HC • (δ,σ) (H). We now recall the cyclic cohomology of a small k-linear category due to McCarthy [CITATION_1] . The additive cyclic nerve of a small k-linear category C is defined to be the cyclic module determined by",
